  <metadata>
    <id>screen-inu</id>
    <version>0.2.3</version>
    <title>Screen Inu</title>
    <authors>ImL1s</authors>
    <projectUrl>https://github.com/ImL1s/screen_inu</projectUrl>
    <tags>screen-inu ocr screenshot productivity utility tauri</tags>
    <summary>Modern screenshot OCR tool.</summary>
    <description>
      Screen Inu is a modern cross-platform screenshot OCR tool built with Tauri (Rust + React).
      
      ## Features
      - **One-Keyboard Shortcut**: (Ctrl/Cmd + Shift + X) to capture immediately.
      - **Instant OCR**: Extract text from any region on your screen.
      - **Multi-Language**: Support for English, Chinese, Japanese, Korean, and more.
      - **Privacy First**: Offline processing (default) using Tesseract.
    </description>
  </metadata>
